<%= scope(:popover_default_content, name: :template, label: "Template and Input").render do %>
  <p>Use your <a href="https://shopify.github.io/liquid">Liquid</a> template to design the look and feel -- along with associated data -- for the screen that will dynamically be built for your device(s). See the URLs and/or Input documentation to understand what objects are available to your template.</p>

  <p>Model information is provided in the form of CSS screen classes via <code>{{extension.css_classes}}</code> which allows you to reuse this template across multiple models when dynamically rendering screens.</p>
<% end %>
